    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget ride to get you from A to B? This no-frills vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 and we're being completely upfront with you! This car shows significant wear both inside and out, and has known mechanical issues that will need attention. It's best suited for a handy buyer or someone looking for a project car on a tight budget. What you see is what you get \u2014 honest pricing, no surprises!",
