    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Here's a fantastic opportunity to drive home a well-cared-for vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, handles with confidence, and has clearly been given the attention it deserves over the years. You'll notice only minor cosmetic blemishes that come naturally with regular use, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. Whether you're commuting daily or heading out on a weekend adventure, this dependable ride is ready to deliver. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in good condition, and the asking price reflects that honestly \u2014 please read this full description before reaching out. The car is in solid, reliable shape with no major mechanical issues. It starts consistently, drives smoothly, and has been maintained adequately over its life. You can expect normal wear consistent with a used vehicle of this age \u2014 some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior such as small scratches or light scuffs, and interior surfaces show everyday use but nothing excessive. All primary systems including engine, transmission, brakes, and cooling are functioning properly. There are no warning lights on the dashboard and no known outstanding repairs needed. This is a dependable daily driver that won't surprise you with immediate costly fixes. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged \u2014 we have nothing to hide. Overall, this is a honest, well-priced vehicle for a buyer looking for reliable transportation without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent about what you're purchasing. The exterior shows heavy wear throughout \u2014 expect multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and paint that has faded and peeled in several areas. The body panels show signs of rust in spots, and the overall appearance reflects years of hard use. Inside, the cabin is worn with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard trim, and general grime that has built up over time. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 buyers should budget for repairs and should have a trusted mechanic inspect the vehicle before purchase. This listing is best suited for someone looking for a project car, a parts vehicle, or a buyer comfortable with taking on significant repair work. We are pricing accordingly and encourage all serious buyers to inspect in person so there are no surprises.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in fair condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a clear, accurate picture before making contact. The exterior shows noticeable wear consistent with its age \u2014 expect some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in areas, though the overall body structure is intact with no major rust or collision damage. The interior is functional but worn, with some scuffs on the trim, seat fabric showing use, and a few small cosmetic imperfections on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks \u2014 it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term, such as worn brake components or aging belts and hoses. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, cooling, and electrical \u2014 are operational. This is a solid choice for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and doesn't mind a vehicle that shows its history, or for someone handy who wants a project with good bones. No major hidden issues \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    }
